# UE5 Generated / Build Artifacts
# --------------------------------------------
Binaries/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Saved/
Build/

# --------------------------------------------
# Content (keep only source assets, ignore cooked)
# --------------------------------------------
# Uncomment if you want to ignore cooked content
# *_BuiltData.uasset

# --------------------------------------------
# Platform Specific
# --------------------------------------------
*.xcodeproj
*.xcworkspace

# --------------------------------------------
# OS generated files
# --------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# --------------------------------------------
# Misc
# --------------------------------------------
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
*.pdb
*.exp
*.obj
*.pyc
__pycache__/
